</del><ab facs="#facs_54_r3l13"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / Vns ıſt cʒevviſſen getan <expan>vvord<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vvie ew <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Hawbtman </ab><ab facs="#facs_54_r3l15">von des Lantfrıds 
<add><ab facs="#facs_54_r3l14"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / daʒ Jr <expan>yecʒunde<ex>n</ex></expan> auf den Lantfrıd </ab><ab facs="#facs_54_r3l16">gen <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüllet / do er <expan>awſſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> handlung </ab><ab facs="#facs_54_r3l17"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / als ſich dann <expan>v<ex>er</ex>loffe<ex>n</ex></expan> hat / do <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Lantfrıd in <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> veld was / </ab><ab facs="#facs_54_r3l19">Nu ıſt vnſer <expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> daʒ Jr das tün ſüllet / Vnd 
